Popular movie director, Charles Novia, lost his mother on the 31st of December 2018. He announced the incident on his social media page, where he revealed how is mother was to him and how he will miss her. He wrote: She passed away in the early hours of the 31st of December 2018.
Mummy. Mother. Friend.
You were more than a mother. And a mother to all.
Teacher. My rock. My world.
Your memories will forever remain.
And that glowing smile…. Clara Osayuware Uwaifo… Rest, My Mother. Rest.